157
00:15:21,004 --> 00:15:23,006
[Woman]
I'm gonna get youl

158
00:15:24,007 --> 00:15:28,011
[Children Chattering,
Laughing]

159
00:15:31,014 --> 00:15:34,017
[Thunder Rumbling]

160
00:15:39,982 --> 00:15:42,985
- [Woman] Hurry up.
- [Child Laughing]

161
00:16:09,011 --> 00:16:13,015
[Thunder Rumbling]

162
00:16:35,996 --> 00:16:41,001
[Thunder Rumbling]

163
00:17:15,994 --> 00:17:18,997
[Panting]

164
00:17:30,008 --> 00:17:34,012
[Panting]

165
00:17:34,012 --> 00:17:37,015
- Come on.
- You're doing it wrong!

166
00:17:39,017 --> 00:17:41,019
It's the way I did it
on the other side!

167
00:17:41,019 --> 00:17:43,981
Nope.
That don't go there.

168
00:17:44,982 --> 00:17:48,986
You're doing it wrong.
Let me show you how to do it.

169
00:17:48,986 --> 00:17:50,988
- That's not what the instructions say.
- Nope. That don't go there.

170
00:17:50,988 --> 00:17:53,991
Let me show you how to do it.

171
00:17:53,991 --> 00:17:56,994
Tie the line to the tree.
Make it high enough...

172
00:17:56,994 --> 00:17:58,996
so you don't kill yourself
in the middle of the night.

173
00:17:58,996 --> 00:18:01,999
I kind of wish I had
one of those old canvas jobs...

174
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:07,004
that you pitch from the inside!

175
00:18:07,004 --> 00:18:10,007
I take it this isn't
your first time pitching a...

176
00:18:12,009 --> 00:18:13,010
tent.

177
00:18:15,012 --> 00:18:18,015
[Groaning, Panting]

178
00:18:30,986 --> 00:18:33,989
[Wind Whistling]

179
00:18:39,995 --> 00:18:42,998
[Thunder Rumbling]

180
00:18:47,002 --> 00:18:49,004
[Sighs]

181
00:19:12,986 --> 00:19:15,989
Please, God...

182
00:19:15,989 --> 00:19:17,991
don't let me die here.

183
00:19:29,002 --> 00:19:32,005
[Audience Applauding]

184
00:19:37,010 --> 00:19:39,012
[Neale] To God,
there is no separation...

185
00:19:39,012 --> 00:19:42,015
between financial abundance
and spirituality.

186
00:19:42,015 --> 00:19:45,018
In fact, they go hand in hand.

187
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:48,981
Don't you find it odd
that we live...

188
00:19:48,981 --> 00:19:52,985
in a society that devalues
our most important jobs?

189
00:19:52,985 --> 00:19:55,988
- What do you mean by that?
- [Neale] I mean, we have no problem...

190
00:19:55,988 --> 00:19:58,991
giving a football coach
five million a season...

191
00:19:58,991 --> 00:20:00,993
or-or an actor
10 million per movie...

192
00:20:00,993 --> 00:20:03,996
but somehow we've got it wired...

193
00:20:03,996 --> 00:20:05,998
where people involved
with spirituality...

194
00:20:05,998 --> 00:20:08,000
should be penniless,
celibate and-and abstinent.

195
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:11,003
[Applause]

196
00:20:11,003 --> 00:20:13,005
- And preferably all three, you know?
- [Audience Laughing]

197
00:20:13,005 --> 00:20:15,007
- [Woman] Yeah. Right.
- I mean, I don't know about you...

198
00:20:15,007 --> 00:20:18,010
but l-I don't– I don't remember
voting for any of that.

199
00:20:18,010 --> 00:20:22,014
- [Audience] No.
- So imagine a world...

200
00:20:22,014 --> 00:20:27,019
where money was given
to people who give us the biggest gifts.

201
00:20:27,019 --> 00:20:29,021
- Teachers.
- [Woman] Oh, yes.

202
00:20:29,021 --> 00:20:30,981
- Artists.
- [Audience] Yes.

203
00:20:30,981 --> 00:20:32,983
- Nurses.
- Yes.

204
00:20:33,984 --> 00:20:36,987
Uh, firemen.
You know, policemen.

205
00:20:36,987 --> 00:20:39,990
- Writers.
- [Laughing]

206
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:42,993
- And mothers!
- [Audience Affirming]

207
00:20:42,993 --> 00:20:44,995
[Woman]
Mothers. That's right.

208
00:20:44,995 --> 00:20:46,997
Yes.

209
00:20:48,999 --> 00:20:52,002
People who connect us,
not disconnect...

210
00:20:52,002 --> 00:20:54,004
or-or-or distract us, you know.

211
00:20:54,004 --> 00:20:57,007
Imagine that world.

212
00:20:57,007 --> 00:20:59,009
And we can have it,
because, people...

213
00:21:00,010 --> 00:21:01,011
we're the ones.

214
00:21:02,012 --> 00:21:06,016
We've always been the ones
that we've been waiting for.

215
00:21:06,016 --> 00:21:10,020
We are. We are.

216
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:12,981
- [Applause Continues]
- [Woman] Yeahl

217
00:21:15,984 --> 00:21:17,986
[Applause Fades]

